<div class="container m-t-70">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-5">
            <div class="profile-left">
                <div class="user-info">
                    <div class="img"><img src="/images/pro-img.jpg"></div>
                    <span class="username">{{user.username}}</span>
                </div>
                <ul class="nav nav-pills nav-stacked b bg-white m-b-xs">
                    <li><a href="javascript:void(0)"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-user m-r-xs"></span>个人资料设置</a></li>
                    <li class="active"><a href="javascript:void(0)"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-lock m-r-xs"></span>修改密码</a></li>
                    <li><a href="javascript:void(0)"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-retweet m-r-xs"></span>帐号绑定</a></li>
                </ul>
                <div class="feature">
                    <a>
                        <div class="help b">
                            <div class="img-icon"></div>
                            <span class="text">使用帮助</span>
                        </div>
                    </a>
                    <a>
                        <div class="about b">
                            <div class="img-icon"></div>
                            <span class="text">关于我们</span>
                        </div>
                    </a>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-white p-h-sm p-v-sm b text-center f-gray m-b-lg">
                    <p>你也可以直接拨打电话
                        或发送邮件联系我们</p>
                    <p>400-4000-4000</p>
                    <p>kuando@163.com</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-19">
            <div class="bg-white p-h-lg profile-activity">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-md-24">
                        <div class="line">
                            <span class="f-gray f-s-20"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-lock m-r-xs"></span>修改密码</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-24 m-t-lg">

                        <div class="row">
                            <div class="col-md-24">
                                <div class="alert alert-warning" role="alert">
                                    如果您是手机 + 验证码 或者 第三方帐号(腾讯、新浪微博等)登录且尚未设定旧密码，可以点击
                                    <a href="#" class="alert-link">重设密码</a>链接.
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-md-12 col-sm-24">
                                <form class="form-horizontal">
                                    <div class="form-group m-t-lg">
                                        <label class="control-label col-md-6">旧密码</label>
                                        <div class="col-md-18">
                                            <input class="form-control" type="text" placeholder="请输入旧密码">
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="form-group m-t-lg">
                                        <label class="control-label col-md-6">新密码</label>
                                        <div class="col-md-18">
                                            <input class="form-control" type="text" placeholder="请输入新密码，限6~20字符">
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="form-group m-t-lg">
                                        <label class="control-label col-md-6">确认新密码</label>
                                        <div class="col-md-18">
                                            <input class="form-control" type="text" placeholder="限6~20字符">
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="form-group m-t-lg">
                                        <div class="col-md-offset-11 col-md-4">
                                            <button class="btn btn-success">确认修改</button>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </form>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>